@* Modals Start*@
<!-- Modal 1-->
<div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop1" data-backdrop="static" data-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-dialog-scrollable modal-lg">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="staticBackdropLabel">About Us</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8">
                        In the quaint town of California, nestled between rolling hills and picturesque landscapes, the sweet legacy of our timeless ice cream shop began in 1950. It was in this charming setting that a young and ambitious entrepreneur, Mr. A, embarked on a journey that would transform his passion for ice cream into a cherished tradition for generations to come.

                        Born into a family with a deep appreciation for culinary arts, Mr. A discovered his love for crafting delectable treats at an early age. At the tender age of 14, armed with determination and a dream, he opened the doors of his modest ice cream shop. His vision was simple yet profound – to share the joy of exquisite flavors with the community and create a space where people could indulge in the timeless pleasure of ice cream.

                        In those early days, Mr. A personally concocted each batch of ice cream, meticulously selecting the finest ingredients and infusing his creations with a genuine passion for the craft. The shop quickly became a local hotspot, drawing in residents from far and wide who were eager to experience the unique blend of tradition and innovation that defined Mr. A's creations.

                        As the years unfolded, so did the success of the ice cream shop. Mr. A's commitment to quality and innovation resonated with patrons, and the shop became a beloved institution in the community. His relentless pursuit of perfection led to the development of signature flavors that became synonymous with the establishment, captivating the taste buds of ice cream enthusiasts.

                        Over the decades, the once modest ice cream shop expanded, transforming into a destination that attracted visitors from neighboring towns and beyond. Mr. A's commitment to preserving the essence of his craft remained unwavering, ensuring that every scoop continued to carry the spirit of his original vision.

                        Today, as our ice cream shop stands as a testament to Mr. A's dedication and entrepreneurial spirit, we invite you to immerse yourself in the rich history and flavors that have defined us for over seven decades. Each scoop is not just a taste of ice cream; it is a journey through time, a celebration of tradition, and an experience of unparalleled satisfaction – a legacy that began with a 14-year-old dreamer in 1950 and has since grown into an enduring symbol of sweetness and joy.
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12">
                                <img src="~/Website/img/mra.jpg" width="inherit" height="350px"></img>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

